NAME
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Size - Determine the sane terminal size

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Size (from Perl distribution
    Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Size), released on 2020-06-05.

DESCRIPTION
PROVIDED METHODS
  termattr_height
    Try to determine the sane terminal height. First observe the "LINES"
    environment variable, if unset then try using Term::Size to determine
    the terminal size, if fail then use default of 25.

  termattr_width
    Try to determine the sane terminal width. First observe the "COLUMNS"
    environment variable, if unset then try using Term::Size to determine
    the terminal size, if fail then use default of 80 (79 on Windows).

